{"tid":1546623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"三毛國師教你港獨？","createTime":"2019-09-06T10:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T10:48:58.000Z","uid":118951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c32436fe075dce76a7b18551f5031d9cf321c03e","tid":1546623,"uid":118951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"其實佢講得都好中下，港人治港套制度之下只要<strong>再加上雙普選 就已經好接近獨立</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVEUA9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVEUA9w.jpg&h=81da5bb1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n所以中共其實成日打開口牌叫你唔好咁做<br />\n敵人反對的...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJWPqfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJWPqfw.jpg&h=aee0b574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而對於雙普選呢個訴求中共係點回應既呢？<br />\n...好L長，其實唔需要睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...重點係佢<strong>無直接否定普選訴求</strong>、而只係講左一堆技術野同假普選既原則<br />\n要再提醒大家一次；<strong>基本法其實係承諾左最終達至普選</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以普選訴求既合法、合理同正當性使得中共無辦法否定&quot;普選&quot;呢樣野本身，只能偷換概念<br />\n所以大家識得用咩黎做盾未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AYBsbXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAYBsbXQ.jpg&h=399b4620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文字：<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4412478072645665?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4412478072645665%3F&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=110e73bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4412478072645665?</a><br />\n影片：<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4412711930406324?#&amp;video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4412711930406324%3F%23%26video&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrxV